# Local Site Context (example)

This file documents your real server details (IP, SSH key path, domains, etc).

- Copy this file to `runbooks/site.local.md`
- Fill it with your actual values
- `runbooks/site.local.md` is ignored by Git (see `.gitignore`)

```
MC_SERVER_HOST=192.0.2.10
MC_SSH_USER=linux
MC_PROJECT_DIR=/home/linux/codex-cobblemon
MC_SERVICE_NAME=cobblemon
MC_PORT=25565

DUCKDNS_DOMAIN=example.duckdns.org

SSH_KEY_MAIN=C:\\Users\\<You>\\.ssh\\mc_admin_<alias>
SSH_KEY_EMERGENCY=C:\\Users\\<You>\\.ssh\\mc_admin_emergency_<alias>

DEFAULT_PLAYER_NAME=YourPlayerName
```
